    public class RecurringActivity
extends Activity
implements org.incode.module.note.dom.api.notable.Notable
    An Activity that is used to schedule individual ActivityEvent objects. The term 'activity' is used in this domain in both a generic and specific way, the term 'event' is not used but is more descriptive of what is occurring, that is a series of calendar events make up a recurring activity.
